{"tid":2266437,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰三示威領袖准保釋 警強行再拘捕  勒頸帶走 一人失知覺","createTime":"2020-11-01T10:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T11:04:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b80343a8dd5dbbc5d86f85480fad43c452bcc037","tid":2266437,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:10:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201101/P4XKLSRYHRERFEE7ZG4AWRFATQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201101%2FP4XKLSRYHRERFEE7ZG4AWRFATQ%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh7rngSbsgLaTM31cPJ1174U%3D&h=9e95360f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201101%2FP4XKLSRYHRERFEE7ZG4AWRFATQ%2F&h=83b85d98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201101/P4XKLSRYHRERFEE7ZG4AWRFATQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n泰三示威領袖准保釋 警強行再拘捕 <br />\n勒頸帶走 一人失知覺<br />\n<br />\n泰國示威持續三個月，政府圖藉拘押示威領袖平息運動，但前日法院終於批准被關押超過半個月的三名示威領袖保釋。惟警方不從，傍晚趕到拘留所再次拘捕三人，據指其間曾用勒頸手法，將其中一人勒至失去知覺，三人昨凌晨先後送院。警方矢言尋求法院再頒拘留令。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：畢業生放紙板異見者 向泰王抗議<br />\n<br />\n巴利（Parit Chiwarak）、帕努莎亞（Panusaya Sithijirawattanakul）與帕努蓬（Panupong Jaadnok）自上月中已被警方以煽動罪名拘禁，多次申請保釋，至前日下午終於獲批。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bjJQpvnfnXEvaZtFt6-1pNWyiBM=/720x496/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K4RHIV643NHRZASF4IKEY4XOXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbjJQpvnfnXEvaZtFt6-1pNWyiBM%3D%2F720x496%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK4RHIV643NHRZASF4IKEY4XOXQ.jpg&h=2ea4fdf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■帕努蓬被警方勒頸後失去知覺。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指涉三府示威<br />\n<br />\n《曼谷郵報》引述「泰國人權律師」（TLHR）組織指，律師前晚抵曼谷拘留所後，發現警方派員到場欲再次拘人，於是展開交涉。警方揚言是就三人涉暖武里、大城與烏汶三個府的示威活動，執行三府所發的拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n但交涉期間，警方趁律師不覺，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方客貨車約9時半到達警署，但警察見現場有數十示威領袖的支持者在場，因此。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n群情洶湧下，警員最初未有強行將巴利與帕努莎亞帶入警署，兩名領袖與支持者在警。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至午夜過後，來自曼谷以北大城的警員到場，兩名領袖被帶返警署問話，至清晨4時半左右，兩人送院。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZQ7WtJns0KMQiekPpCU1R6dK74Q=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EVGJ5QOTDNBRPAT7JV6COI6X7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZQ7WtJns0KMQiekPpCU1R6dK74Q%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEVGJ5QOTDNBRPAT7JV6COI6X7A.jpg&h=86532be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■帕努莎亞（左）與巴利（右）前晚在警局外向支持者講話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警矢言出院即拉<br />\n<br />\n陪同巴利和帕努莎亞送院的醫生兼前國會議員托沙蓬指：「他倆在問話後都疲累虛弱，相信要留院兩三天觀察。」他另指巴利在警方客貨車上被玻璃碎輕微割傷。泰國傳媒指，事緣有支持者從拘留所一路追蹤警方客貨車，發現帕努蓬失去知覺後，心急地攔車並砸破車窗玻璃。警車為避開他們，將路邊兩架電單車分別拖跌和拖行。<br />\n<br />\n警方表明會尋求法院再頒令，誓要在三名示威領袖甫出院就立即將他們再次拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/泰國《曼谷郵報》"},{"pid":"9aa90199e89dc94bc15f2959b5030df43af6a095","tid":2266437,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:14:26.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cbef64252ef7286bb19d0d011f2b7b01d815e4","tid":2266437,"uid":55581,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"天下黑警一樣黑"},{"pid":"438108cadf169ef6c0fa8d9e247c465df1205513","tid":2266437,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"4429a139fe846308eaf5784170ca748279f4fed2","tid":2266437,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52cbef64252ef7286bb19d0d011f2b7b01d815e4","tid":2266437,"uid":55581,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"天下黑警一樣黑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a